{"id": "ChIJjYU8IQvHwoARAxpf-BPTQx8", "rating": 4.3, "userRatingCount": 169, "displayName": {"text": "HARUCAKE", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJjYU8IQvHwoARAxpf-BPTQx8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CelYxTllSbWRDTkVselIxcEtiREZhTFU5RmRIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Harucake is my fave place to treat myself to after a while or bring guests to whenever they come visit. They added a soosoo matcha to their menu and I was bouncing off the walls since I've been wanting to give it a try, but could not try their soosoo latte since I don't like coffee. It was just as amazing as I expected and wish I could drink it every day.\n\nTheir cakes are delectable and not too sweet. My fave is their injeolmi cake- the perfect balance of sweet and salty with an addicting nutty scent.\n\nI've recently tried their dubai chewy cookie and was not a huge fan- $10 each was quite a steep price point for a treat that didn't quite live up to the hype, unfortunately.\n\nService is always pretty quick and friendly! I just wish they were open on Sundays as well :')", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Harucake is my fave place to treat myself to after a while or bring guests to whenever they come visit. They added a soosoo matcha to their menu and I was bouncing off the walls since I've been wanting to give it a try, but could not try their soosoo latte since I don't like coffee. It was just as amazing as I expected and wish I could drink it every day.\n\nTheir cakes are delectable and not too sweet. My fave is their injeolmi cake- the perfect balance of sweet and salty with an addicting nutty scent.\n\nI've recently tried their dubai chewy cookie and was not a huge fan- $10 each was quite a steep price point for a treat that didn't quite live up to the hype, unfortunately.\n\nService is always pretty quick and friendly! I just wish they were open on Sundays as well :')", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "S J", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106932596816032884304/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVd_Zqc5NjnSnHRjHQRlTRUe_nd57Wuu6B1gNUsgL312qv_NC8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-21T04:56:30.242530873Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CelYxTllSbWRDTkVselIxcEtiREZhTFU5RmRIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CelYxTllSbWRDTkVselIxcEtiREZhTFU5RmRIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c70b213c858d:0x1f43d313f85f1a03"}, {"name": "places/ChIJjYU8IQvHwoARAxpf-BPTQx8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5Slp5MTJSREl6VDBaVGJUQXlhRkkxZVZOTldVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Harucake is usually very busy during the day and evening, so I visited early in the morning to avoid the long lines.\n\nThe plaza offers valet parking, but in the morning it was quiet enough that parking was free, which made the visit more convenient. The bakery is known for its fresh cream cakes and choux pastries, which are made to order. Because of this, many customers place orders online and come in for pickup.\n\nPrices are on the higher side, but the freshness is noticeable. I tried the egg tart, and it paired perfectly with a morning coffee — a simple but enjoyable treat.\n\nOverall, a great spot if you visit early and want to enjoy fresh desserts without the crowds.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Harucake is usually very busy during the day and evening, so I visited early in the morning to avoid the long lines.\n\nThe plaza offers valet parking, but in the morning it was quiet enough that parking was free, which made the visit more convenient. The bakery is known for its fresh cream cakes and choux pastries, which are made to order. Because of this, many customers place orders online and come in for pickup.\n\nPrices are on the higher side, but the freshness is noticeable. I tried the egg tart, and it paired perfectly with a morning coffee — a simple but enjoyable treat.\n\nOverall, a great spot if you visit early and want to enjoy fresh desserts without the crowds.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ahacool Kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107771775586078041551/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWII91BLScs7M7RWArxVYsddhX6V7Zx9ukobFEyPWUquvz9JLjy=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-03T18:18:53.189594793Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5Slp5MTJSREl6VDBaVGJUQXlhRkkxZVZOTldVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5Slp5MTJSREl6VDBaVGJUQXlhRkkxZVZOTldVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c70b213c858d:0x1f43d313f85f1a03"}, {"name": "places/ChIJjYU8IQvHwoARAxpf-BPTQx8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCMk0wcFRibk5tYkZGM2FrcGhWV040VDJWdldVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The soosoo matcha and hojicha drinks are soo good especially if you like corn flavors! The corn cream and corn ice cream are amazing I always come back for it... Their cakes are pricy but very tasty too ive liked every flavor, not too sweet and very soft and creamy.\n\nThe original egg tart is also really good, super flaky on the outside and soft egg on the inside. For the scones I prefer the plain milk cream flavor. The corn one was good too but the ones with icing on top of the scone were too much for me. The milk cream is really soft and not too sweet.\n\nThe new dubai chocolate mochi ball is good but I probably wouldn't get it again for 10 dollars, it's nice to try once though.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The soosoo matcha and hojicha drinks are soo good especially if you like corn flavors! The corn cream and corn ice cream are amazing I always come back for it... Their cakes are pricy but very tasty too ive liked every flavor, not too sweet and very soft and creamy.\n\nThe original egg tart is also really good, super flaky on the outside and soft egg on the inside. For the scones I prefer the plain milk cream flavor. The corn one was good too but the ones with icing on top of the scone were too much for me. The milk cream is really soft and not too sweet.\n\nThe new dubai chocolate mochi ball is good but I probably wouldn't get it again for 10 dollars, it's nice to try once though.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Elaine Wang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108149311943287199389/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULV3jTJ9wcLdbVooMhB0YHf-cWnf8R7T9Pu2c_tMQcF3dzPzq4Ww=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-14T21:33:04.630663553Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCMk0wcFRibk5tYkZGM2FrcGhWV040VDJWdldVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCMk0wcFRibk5tYkZGM2FrcGhWV040VDJWdldVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c70b213c858d:0x1f43d313f85f1a03"}, {"name": "places/ChIJjYU8IQvHwoARAxpf-BPTQx8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1TlgyUkVhekpaUlVzNFZuWk9kVTlVYlZvM01WRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "A very unique dessert shop with great flavors. The popular items sell out quickly! I had a short chat with the manager and learned about their careful ingredient sourcing, which made me appreciate the place even more. I especially loved the Harucake-definitely worth trying.\nOnly one thing: hard to park", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "A very unique dessert shop with great flavors. The popular items sell out quickly! I had a short chat with the manager and learned about their careful ingredient sourcing, which made me appreciate the place even more. I especially loved the Harucake-definitely worth trying.\nOnly one thing: hard to park", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "B Shine", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103946835254755503852/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7jm4xTcT_29Bj49RoC-Jq2K3dALXc5dhpQM4utrb7KPoU7dBG=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-10T06:07:35.450761241Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1TlgyUkVhekpaUlVzNFZuWk9kVTlVYlZvM01WRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1TlgyUkVhekpaUlVzNFZuWk9kVTlVYlZvM01WRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c70b213c858d:0x1f43d313f85f1a03"}, {"name": "places/ChIJjYU8IQvHwoARAxpf-BPTQx8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGb2JHSjVTakZVV0UwNVFXaENhR3BzZUZGNWFGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This is a really cafe in Ktown. They’re most known for their specialty drinks and cakes. We got the Soosoo matcha and Soosoo lattes, which are basically corn flavored einspanners with a corn ice cream on top. The flavors of the drinks were really lovely without being too sweet. They also use real corn in the drink!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is a really cafe in Ktown. They’re most known for their specialty drinks and cakes. We got the Soosoo matcha and Soosoo lattes, which are basically corn flavored einspanners with a corn ice cream on top. The flavors of the drinks were really lovely without being too sweet. They also use real corn in the drink!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lydia Cheng", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107788647573598966694/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFHB_U6gdE25WZAuVb9zVpFjbC